data.text: @ZoePrecious2020 It will be denied. We’ve already got many many reports of very serious short time side effects and they are  at best being cast as either inaccurate and unreliable from official sources or at worst, labelled disinformation. Won’t change. Will only get worse.

@ZoePrecious2020 If you were paying attention the “experts” have said you can still get it & transmit it even after you get the jab; AND, you still have to wear a mask & social distance. Therefore it does not protect anyone.
